[SN]TITLE[SN]
David Hasselhoff fan meets idol in Wolverhampton

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A life-long David Hasselhoff fan was able to meet her idol when he appeared on stage in the West Midlands.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
18 November 2015 Last updated at 17:56 GMT
The former Baywatch actor is playing the role of Ross in Last Night a DJ Saved My Life at the Wolverhampton Grand Theatre.
Maria McRee, from Telford, Shropshire, went to see the production and was introduced to the 63-year-old - nicknamed The Hoff - by BBC Midlands Today reporter Satnam Rana.
